This has to be done with Javascript, Blade outputs the HTML way before your Javascript loads or input change

Here&#39;s an example (not to copy paste)

```html
@foreach($notes as $note)

&lt;h2 hidden&gt;{{ $note-&gt;name }}&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;input id=&quot;number&quot; name=&quot;number&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;

